ting\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cctvaatl\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21f4ff356c8ae28dc944a1a9370fb426?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21f4ff356c8ae28dc944a1a9370fb426?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cctvaatl\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cctvaatl</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Our company purchased events calendar pro and the filter bar to sell courses online rather than go down the whole woocommerce route. We use the free tickets plugin and sell using the built in paypal option. My knowledge of wordpress is limited and initially I needed advice on how to customise events calendar to suit our business needs. I was not familiar with editing strings/translations etc. I read through the knowledge base articles but found these a little overwhelming and decided to email support for guidance. Over the space of a few days the support team (big thank you to Deblyn) provided all the advice/tips I needed to make the necessary changes to events calendar. I am using the legacy templates rather the upgraded templates and these work just fine for our needs and still look great. If you are looking to sell tickets to live events or seats on face to face training courses then I would not hesitate to recommend events calendar. All good products are usually complimented by good after sales support and events calendar did not disappoint. Once again many thanks to Deblyn for sharing his knowledge especially the tip on Say What! Thank you.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Possibly the worst plugin I have used</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bsweb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64b60211a62acbfae847bdcd6e2066f2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64b60211a62acbfae847bdcd6e2066f2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bsweb\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bsweb</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Unstable, constant bugs, make you do the debugging, they change the CSS classes almost every release so customisations break constantly, they put css in the footer as well as the header and just generally awful. And this is a paid product. Avoid.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">the best calendar</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bigbear67\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bd69907c256e50841401265c41d24095?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bd69907c256e50841401265c41d24095?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bigbear67\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bigbear67</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 1, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">for all our event that is the best</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thank you!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danailies\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42563b27fc996e49ff0b5a7d39d5a38c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/42563b27fc996e49ff0b5a7d39d5a38c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danailies\" class=\"reviewer-name\">danailies</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">มิถุนายน 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am very happy with it!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Garbage</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/benoitadam\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f1c99c186102fd69ab692e42d841b48d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f1c99c186102fd69ab692e42d841b48d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/benoitadam\" class=\"reviewer-name\">benoitadam</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">มิถุนายน 23, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">TONS of options but no events shows-up in the \"event\" page.\n\nWhat\'s the point of this plugin if you can\'t do the most primitive stuff ?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best we&#039;ve tested</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/malchcik\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21d9ba27bf1ad6c32e178eddb9970cc5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/21d9ba27bf1ad6c32e178eddb9970cc5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/malchcik\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Malchcik</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">มิถุนายน 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We\'re using calendars on several websites, and tested quite a few plugins before implementing The Events Calendar.  It was the best all-around mix of features, UI design, and customizability.  We\'re also making use of the API in a complex use case.  Solid product with extensive documentation.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does what it says.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/garc964\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e746b539b82d7aa51afaf594f01c99f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e746b539b82d7aa51afaf594f01c99f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/garc964\" class=\"reviewer-name\">garc964</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">มิถุนายน 19, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">2 years of use and no problems encountered.\nOur site only publishes basic events nothing fancy no interactions. \nIf I remember correctly the calender doesn\'t allow HTML formatting in the title.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Top notch calendar plugin with EXCELLENT support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juleswebb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/594a4c6b2dc0905bbcc2f7a505d1ba5b?s=16&#038;d=monst