iew-body\">not user friendly at all</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not impressed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anickafil\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/671b6c9983a479b530ad20a9c87e467e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/671b6c9983a479b530ad20a9c87e467e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anickafil\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anickafil</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Tried but not meeting my requirements. \nDeleted all forms but after deactivation, installed a different plugin, t gives me the following:\n\nContact Form Redirection\nError: Please install and activate Contact Form 7.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Love Hate Relationship</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thehowarde\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d1f97c29b362df4e40a87c3d4e4c53d8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d1f97c29b362df4e40a87c3d4e4c53d8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thehowarde\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thehowarde</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">While I develop themes, and use this plugin extensively, the primary developer is somewhat of a dick with his attitude towards backwards compatibility, and frequently forces updates that cause old sites to break, or cease to function. No warnings of these changes, just surprise ah-ha, you you have to go and fix a client site for free, since the stuff used to work, but now doesn\'t.  Major version updates usually mean you have to check forms actually still work after they\'re submitted.   </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Failed to send email with reCaptcha v3</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akjiainc\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6d0211d65470faf616164fed57f826b2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6d0211d65470faf616164fed57f826b2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akjiainc\" class=\"reviewer-name\">akjiainc</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Just find it failed sending messgae because of the reCaptcha v3 issue. when I disable the reCaptcha v3, it works again.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Using this plugin has probably cost me customers</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adamford\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/811ba1af67cfd9850c941ab5626fa919?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/811ba1af67cfd9850c941ab5626fa919?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adamford\" class=\"reviewer-name\">adamford</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It appears that around 6 months ago this plugin stopped randomly working on my site on mobile devices and it appears some desktop ones as well. So goodness only knows how many lead enquiries it has cost me. Then when I submitted a support ticket, nobody has ever even bothered responding. So thanks for ruining my website and not caring.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">easy to use contact form plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/deschampsy\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/00f5279fd9001bb90a41a88947720ad1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/00f5279fd9001bb90a41a88947720ad1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/deschampsy\" class=\"reviewer-name\">deschampsy</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">กรกฎาคม 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">at the beginning I had some problems with the custom fields integration, but with the help of the support all worked out pretty well.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent Plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brunods\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fcd81ccca89a72dc4cc21a97d047a906?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fcd81ccca89a72dc4cc21a97d047a906?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brunods\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brunods</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">มิถุนายน 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple and strong. 100% recommendable.\nThank you very much for such a great Plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Really good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons da