ting-using-avada/\">How to Automate Your Marketing Using Avada</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theme-fusion.com\">ThemeFusion | Avada Website Builder</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Michael\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27050:\"<div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\"  style=\'background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;\'><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row \"><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1 fusion-builder-column-0 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1\"  style=\'margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\'><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\"><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Using the <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a>, creating the website of your dreams becomes a lot easier. <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> includes a range of tools to help you get your website up and running and market it. The last part is essential if you want to find an audience, and so is knowing what tasks you should automate.</p>\n<p>By ‘automating’ parts of your marketing process, your website will grow more efficiently and free up time for you to focus on other tasks, such as content creation. For example, you could use email marketing platforms to send automated campaigns at crucial moments.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll introduce you to the concept of <a href=\"https://bloggingwizard.com/email-marketing-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">marketing automation</a> and how it works. Then we’ll go over two ways you can implement it using <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a>. Let’s get to it!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Why Marketing Automation is Key to Your Website’s Growth</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Marketing automation is a term that encompasses a lot of practice. “Automation” is the keyword here, since your goal is to use tools to unload a lot of repetitive work off your plate. Some examples of marketing automation include:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-1\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">\n<p><strong>Automated marketing emails.</strong> You can configure some platforms to send pre-designed emails at specific moments, such as welcome messages and purchase confirmations.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">\n<p><strong>Split testing.</strong> With this practice, you create multiple variations of messages or pages and let your marketing software run tests for you to see which one gets the best engagement.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">\n<p><strong>Multi-channel marketing.</strong> Depending on the marketing tools you use, you could connect to your users via SMS, push notifications, social media, and a broad range of additional channels. In most cases, those messages are automated.</p>\n</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Although you can send personalized marketing messages on a case-by-case basis, doing so at scale would take up too much of your time. Marketing automation doesn’t mean the messages or campaigns you send aren’t high quality. <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/turn-your-avada-website-into-a-marketing-powerhouse-with-hubspot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Modern marketing tools</a> provide you with a lot of features to make sure the messages you send are as relevant as possible, including personalization and segmentation.</p>\n<p>Every website prioritizes different marketing approaches. If your primary marketing channel is email, then it makes sense you prioritize automating as many of your campaigns as possible. With <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a>, you get built-in functionality to help you tackle email and other channels more efficiently.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">2 Ways to Automate Your Marketing Using Avada</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>In theory, you can use almost any marketing automation software alongside your website. Given the goal of making your life easier, we’ll focus on options that work seamlessly with both WordPress and Avada so that you can scale your marketing efforts efficiently.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-3 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">1. Collect Leads Using Automated Pop-Ups</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Popups are one of the most effective ways to collect leads through your website. On average, popups can increase your conversion rates by <a href=\"https://sumo.com/stories/pop-up-statistics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">around 3.1%</a>, with high-performing elements getting about 9.3% total.</p>\n<p>Those aren’t numbers to scoff at. However, using popups can be controversial, so you must approach them the right way. Two great examples would be displaying modals to show you offers or to ask you to sign up for an email list:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-1\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor.png\" width=\"1600\" height=\"504\" alt=\"Exit Intent Popups\" title=\"Exit Intent Popups\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758443\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%27504%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201600%20504%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%273504%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor-200x63.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor-400x126.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor-600x189.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor-800x252.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor-1200x378.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/exit-intent-popups-compressor.png 1600w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>These examples are popups built using <a href=\"https://www.convertplug.com/plus/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Convert Plus</a> – a bundled plugin with Avada, designed to help you create high-performing popups. With Convert Plus, you can show exit-intent popups, email opt-ins, limited-time offers, and much more.</p>\n<p>Once you choose a popup style, <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> and <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/theme-features/avada-third-party-integration/convert-plus/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Convert Plus</a> enables you to configure its behavior. In other words, you can decide how the automation works. For example, you can choose whether to display popups a few seconds after visitors load a page, right before they leave, or a combination:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor.png\" width=\"1600\" height=\"659\" alt=\"Smart Launch Settings\" title=\"Smart Launch Settings\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758448\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%27659%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201600%20659%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%273659%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor-200x82.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor-400x165.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor-600x247.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor-800x330.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor-1200x494.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/smart-launch-settings-compressor.png 1600w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>To avoid issues where you keep showing the same popups to the same users, Convert Plus enables you to disable this automation in several ways. You can stop showing popups to users for a set number of days after they close that message or after they convert:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-3\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor.png\" width=\"1600\" height=\"408\" alt=\"Repeat Settings\" title=\"Repeat Settings\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758449\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%27408%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201600%20408%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271600%27%20height%3D%273408%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor-200x51.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor-400x102.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor-600x153.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor-800x204.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor-1200x306.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/repeat-settings-compressor.png 1600w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>In any case, you must remember that while popups can be powerful, they can also impact <a href=\"https://profitblitz.com/monetize-your-blog-without-impacting-user-experience/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">User Experience</a> (UX.) As a rule of thumb, you shouldn’t show visitors more than one popup during their time on your website, or you risk scaring them away.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-4 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">2. Connect a Marketing Automation Platform to WordPress</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Different marketing automation platforms tend to focus on specific communication channels. For example, <a href=\"https://www.activecampaign.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ActiveCampaign</a> is an option that focuses mostly on email marketing and live chat (which can be automated, naturally):</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor.jpg\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1305\" alt=\"ActiveCampaign\" title=\"ActiveCampaign\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758451\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%271305%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201900%201305%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%2731305%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor-200x137.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor-400x275.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor-600x412.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor-800x549.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor-1200x824.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/active-campaign-compressor.jpg 1900w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Another great option is <a href=\"https://www.sendinblue.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sendinblue</a>, which enables you to automate both email and SMS campaigns. Sendinblue also happens to be a very WordPress-friendly option. There’s an <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">official plugin</a> you can use for integrating both platforms:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-5\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor.jpg\" width=\"1900\" height=\"955\" alt=\"Sendinblue\" title=\"Sendinblue\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758455\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%27955%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201900%20955%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%273955%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor-200x101.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor-400x201.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor-600x302.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor-800x402.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor-1200x603.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/sendinblue-compressor.jpg 1900w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>As far as marketing automation goes, however, our favorite option is <a href=\"https://convertkit.com/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ConvertKit</a>. It focuses mostly on email, but it lets you set up highly complex automation workflows:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-6\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit.jpg\" width=\"2684\" height=\"1176\" alt=\"ConvertKit\" title=\"ConvertKit\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758460\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272684%27%20height%3D%271176%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202684%201176%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272684%27%20height%3D%2731176%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-200x88.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-400x175.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-600x263.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-800x351.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-1200x526.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit.jpg 2684w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>ConvertKit integrates out of the box with Convert Plus, which is the tool we used in the last section to help you set up automated popups. You can use Convert Plus to help you collect leads and email signups and ConvertKit to help you manage the marketing end of things.</p>\n<p>ConvertKit provides access to a visual automation workflow builder, which enables you to map out every step of your customer’s journey:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-7\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor.png\" width=\"1737\" height=\"2394\" alt=\"ConvertKit Automations Example\" title=\"ConvertKit Automations Example\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-758464\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271737%27%20height%3D%272394%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201737%202394%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271737%27%20height%3D%2732394%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor-200x276.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor-400x551.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor-600x827.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor-800x1103.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor-1200x1654.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/convertkit-automations-example-compressor.png 1737w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>This level of micromanagement enables you to automate processes such as post-purchase follow-ups, upsells, and downsells. ConvertKit also helps you manage traditional email marketing campaigns – excellent if you’re already using Avada.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-5 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"conclusion\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Conclusion</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>If you want your website to reach its full potential, it needs more than good looks and functionality. The <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a> will help you with both aspects, but content and marketing are still up to you. However, with the right marketing automation tools, this outreach becomes much more straightforward, so you have more time to focus on engaging your audience.</p>\n<p>There are several ways you can automate your marketing using Avada, including:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-2\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Collecting leads using automated popups.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Connecting a marketing automation platform to WordPress.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Do you have any questions about how to approach marketing automation? Ask away in the comments section below!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@merakist?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Merakist</a> on <a href=\"/s/photos/digital-marketing?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Unsplash</a></p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-fullwidth.fusion-bu