,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;\'><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row \"><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1 fusion-builder-column-1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1\"  style=\'margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\'><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\"><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Webinars are one of the most powerful marketing tools at your disposal. A successful webinar can net you dozens or hundreds of new leads, depending on attendance. Unlike other marketing methods, it enables you to engage your live audience and answer their questions in real-time.</p>\n<p>However, knowing how to host a webinar and how to integrate it with your existing website is key to getting those leads. With <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a>, there are several ways you can leverage your website to maximize attendance and ensure your webinars are a success.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll dig deeper into why webinars are such a fantastic marketing tool. Then, we&#8217;ll introduce you to two top <a href=\"https://bloggingwizard.com/webinar-software-platforms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">webinar software</a> options that play nicely with WordPress and talk about how you can use the <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a> to boost your numbers. Let&#8217;s get to it!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-6 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Why Webinars Are an Excellent Marketing Tool</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Websites usually use all sorts of marketing tools, such as email, various forms of content, ads, and much more. However, webinars are a different breed of marketing tools, as they enable you to connect directly with your audience. With a webinar, you can achieve the following:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-3\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Get a rapt audience for the duration of the event.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Answer questions and engage with viewers&#8217; live.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Boost your credibility as an expert in whatever topic you&#8217;re covering.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Beyond that, webinars have a built-in element of exclusivity. Since they&#8217;re <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/how-to-promote-events-on-your-wordpress-website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">one-time events</a>, viewers have to make time to sit and listen to you actively. After they&#8217;ve heard to you for a while, they&#8217;re much more likely to convert.</p>\n<p>&#8216;Successful&#8217; webinars have an average conversion rate of <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/increased-webinar-attendance-one-thing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">about 19%</a> and are unheard of for any marketing channel. Still, the trade-off is that a successful webinar requires a lot of planning. Ideally, you want to rehearse what you&#8217;re going to say, double-check all your facts, consider what questions you might get asked, and more.</p>\n<p>Then there&#8217;s the technical aspect. The platform or tool you use to host your webinar plays a considerable role. Some platforms will make it easier for you to use interactive learning aids, share documents, and other useful features.</p>\n<p>Regardless, your chosen webinar software needs to also integrate with your website. Let&#8217;s discuss this next.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-7 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">2 of the Best Webinar Software Options for Avada and WordPress</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Webinar software is abundant, but we&#8217;re looking for options that integrate well with <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a>, and by extension, WordPress. Here are two top WordPress-friendly webinar platforms we recommend.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">1. <a style=\"color: #292a2c; hover: #65bc7b;\" href=\"https://webinarninja.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Webinar Ninja</a></h3></div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://webinarninja.com/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Webinar Ninja\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor.jpg\" width=\"2916\" height=\"914\" alt=\"Webinar Ninja\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-757454\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272916%27%20height%3D%27914%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202916%20914%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272916%27%20height%3D%273914%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor-200x63.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor-400x125.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor-600x188.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor-800x251.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor-1200x376.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/webinarninja-compressor.jpg 2916w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://webinarninja.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Webinar Ninja</a> enables you to host highly interactive webinars. The platform offers features such as slides, screen sharing, Q&amp;A areas, polls, on-demand offers, and of course, chat. With Webinar Ninja, you can host live events or set up automated webinars for full series. The platform takes care of email notifications for you, too, so you can focus on developing your webinar&#8217;s content.</p>\n<p>You can easily <a href=\"https://zapier.com/apps/webinarninja/integrations/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">connect Webinar Ninja with WordPress</a> using <a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zapier</a>, which supports multiple integration methods. The platform also enables you to embed webinar registration forms into your website, which works flawlessly with <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><i class=\"fb-icon-element-1 fb-icon-element fontawesome-icon fa-comment-dollar fas circle-no fusion-no-small-visibility fusion-text-flow\" style=\"font-size:28px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"></i><style>i.fontawesome-icon.fb-icon-element-1{ color: #65bc7b;}i.fontawesome-icon.fb-icon-element-1:hover { color: #65bc7b;}</style> Plans start at $39 per month for webinars with up to 100 viewers.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-9 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">2. <a style=\"color: #292a2c; hover: #65bc7b;\" href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zoom</a></h3></div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-9\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Zoom\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor.jpg\" width=\"2716\" height=\"760\" alt=\"Zoom\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-757455\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272716%27%20height%3D%27760%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202716%20760%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272716%27%20height%3D%273760%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor-200x56.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor-400x112.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor-600x168.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor-800x224.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor-1200x336.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/zoom-compressor.jpg 2716w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zoom</a> is the name currently on everyone&#8217;s lips. On top of being an excellent option for work video conferencing, you can host webinars that include Q&amp;A sections, polls, and chat. The software also enables attendees to &#8216;raise&#8217; their hands, which makes for a quick way to gauge engagement. You can even promote attendees to panelists in case you want to feature someone with interesting questions.</p>\n<p>There are a lot of ways you can integrate Zoom with WordPress. For starters, there are plugins (such as <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/video-conferencing-with-zoom-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Video Conferencing with Zoom</a>) that enable you to set up pages for upcoming webinars, including elements visitors can use to join.</p>\n<p>You can also use Avada&#8217;s choice of contact form plugin – <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/contact-form-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Contact Form 7</a> – to set up email signup forms for Zoom webinars. In the next section, we&#8217;ll show you an example of a page that uses one of these simple forms.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><i class=\"fb-icon-element-2 fb-icon-element fontawesome-icon fa-comment-dollar fas circle-no fusion-no-small-visibility fusion-text-flow\" style=\"font-size:28px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"></i><style>i.fontawesome-icon.fb-icon-element-2{ color: #65bc7b;}i.fontawesome-icon.fb-icon-element-2:hover { color: #65bc7b;}</style> Zoom plans start at $14.99 per month, and you&#8217;ll also need their Webinar add-on, which costs an extra $40 per month.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-10 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">How to Showcase Your Webinars Using Avada</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>You can&#8217;t have a successful webinar without promotion. Viewers need to know about the event in advance, and you need a way to gauge people&#8217;s interest. As such, your webinar landing page should fulfill three simple criteria:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-4\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Lets visitors know the subject of your webinar and convince them to sign up.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">It provides a signup form so you can collect leads and gauge how many viewers you&#8217;ll have.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Tells users when the event will be.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>With the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a>, it&#8217;s easy to build a high-converting landing page that fulfills all three criteria. If you&#8217;re in a hurry, you can use one of the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/demos/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">prebuilt websites</a> to help you get a landing page ready fast. For example, the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/launch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Launch</a> prebuilt website is perfect for an upcoming webinar, as it includes an email signup form and a countdown timer out of the box:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-10 hover-type-none\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/launch/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Avada Launch\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor.jpg\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1142\" alt=\"Avada Launch\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-757477\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%271142%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201900%201142%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%2731142%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor-200x120.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor-400x240.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor-600x361.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor-800x481.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor-1200x721.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-compressor.jpg 1900w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>All that&#8217;s left for you to do is adjust the landing page to your unique requirements, and doing this is efficient and straight forward with the <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bKyvTW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a>:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-11 hover-type-none\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/launch/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Avada Launch\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor.jpg\" width=\"1900\" height=\"1211\" alt=\"Avada Launch\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-757478\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%271211%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201900%201211%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271900%27%20height%3D%2731211%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor-200x127.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor-400x255.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor-600x382.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor-800x510.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-launch-edit-compressor-1200x765.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/avada-laun