<div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1 fusion-builder-column-19 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1\"  style=\'margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\'><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-50 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"global\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Exploring The Taxi Demo Global Footer</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Let&#8217;s start by examining the <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> Taxi demo&#8217;s custom footer. As illustrated below, a custom Footer Layout Section is set up to display globally across the entire site for all pages and posts.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-38\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[51d1198556b3e0ad02b]\" data-title=\"Taxi Demo Global Footer\" title=\"Taxi Demo Global Footer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"832\" alt=\"Taxi Demo Global Footer\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-703342\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27832%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20832%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273832%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer-200x90.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer-400x180.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer-600x270.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer-800x360.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer-1200x540.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_taxi_custom_global_footer.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Upon editing the Custom Footer Layout, you will notice a four-column layout applying various Design Elements and settings to make up the design of the footer. The number of columns you decide to use is up to you. Anything from one to six columns will work.</p>\n<p>With Custom Layouts, being constrained by WordPress widgets and the Theme Options in the traditional sense is a thing of the past. You can design and build your layouts using the full power of the Avada Website Builder.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-39\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[571a83c7fe689f8509d]\" data-title=\"Taxi Demo Custom Footer Layout Section\" title=\"Taxi Demo Custom Footer Layout Section\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"2096\" alt=\"Taxi Demo Custom Footer Layout Section\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-696666\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%272096%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%202096%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%2732096%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section-200x227.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section-400x453.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section-600x680.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section-800x906.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section-1200x1360.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>And here, you can see what the custom footer looks like on the front end. The only limit will be your imagination.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-40\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_footer_layout_section_front_end.jpg\" class=\"fus