\" alt=\"Single Post Layout Layout Sections\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-703427\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27714%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20714%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273714%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections-200x77.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections-400x154.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections-600x232.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections-800x309.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections-1200x463.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_single_post_layout_sections.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-52 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">A &#8211; The Single Post Title Bar</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The Page Title Bar set up is relatively straight forward. We start with the main container with a background image applied in the container settings, followed by a full-width column with a Title Element (using dynamic content as an option) and a Breadcrumbs Design Element.</p>\n<p>For more information about how to use dynamic content options with Avada, please see this <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/settings-tools/dynamic-content-in-avada/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">help file and video</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-42\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[d92c72feaf7687c6b68]\" data-title=\"Taxi Demo Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Taxi Demo Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"625\" alt=\"Taxi Demo Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-696676\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27625%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20625%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273625%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section-200x68.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section-400x135.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section-600x203.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section-800x270.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section-1200x405.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The image below shows what the Single Post Page Title Bar looks like on the front end.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-43\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[f850f8c571089cd1c54]\" data-title=\"Taxi Demo Front End Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Taxi Demo Front End Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"656\" alt=\"Taxi Demo Front End Custom Page Title Bar Layout Section\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-696677\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27656%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20656%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273656%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end-200x71.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end-400x142.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end-600x213.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end-800x284.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end-1200x426.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_custom_page_title_bar_layout_section_front_end.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-53 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">B &#8211; The Single Post Content</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The Content Layout section for the Single Post has a lot more added to it than the Page Title Bar. The layout uses a combination of <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/avada-design-elements-vs-layout-section-elements/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Layout Elements</a> and Design Elements. The image below clearly shows all of the various facets that make up this custom layout in the Fusion Builder. For more insight into how this built, please watch the <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/videos/how-to-build-a-custom-single-post-layout-video/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How To Build A Custom Single Post Layout video</a>.</p>\n<p>When editing the Layout, you will see a multi Container, multi Column layout—with a combination of Design Elements, Layout Elements, and nested columns, acting as sidebars. It also has a Global Container at the bottom, working as a Call to Action.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=