=\"fusion-text\"><p>The image below shows what the Single Post Content Layout looks like on the front end.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-45\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[16fa072c4cd96dad781]\" data-title=\"Taxi Demo Single Post Content Layout Section Front End\" title=\"Taxi Demo Single Post Content Layout Section Front End\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"3347\" alt=\"Taxi Demo Single Post Content Layout Section Front End\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-696680\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273347%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%203347%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%2733347%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example-200x362.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example-400x724.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example-600x1086.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example-800x1447.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example-1200x2171.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/docs_6.2_taxi_single_post_layout_fe_example.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900