ions.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[c12f8bbe959285f5648]\" data-title=\"Custom 404 Layout Sections\" title=\"Custom 404 Layout Sections\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"713\" alt=\"Custom 404 Layout Sections\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-703441\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27713%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20713%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273713%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections-200x77.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections-400x154.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections-600x231.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections-800x308.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections-1200x462.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_404_layout_sections.jpg 1850w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-55 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">A &#8211; The 404 Page Title Bar</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The Page Title Bar set up is relatively straight forward, but is different from the PTB created for single posts (explained above). We start with the main container with a background image and gradient applied in the container settings, followed by two full-width columns. The first column has a Title Element, followed by a second column that has a Text Block Element and then a call to action Button Element.</p>\n<p>Feel free to check out <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">this page</a> that showcases all of the available Avada Design Elements.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-47\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[5751cecad303c6f008f]\" data-title=\"404 page Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"404 page Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout.jpg\" width=\"1850\" height=\"929\" alt=\"404 page Page Title Bar Layout Section\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-696688\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%27929%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201850%20929%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271850%27%20height%3D%273929%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout-200x100.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout-400x201.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout-600x301.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/docs_6.2_taxi_404_ptb_layout-800x402.jpg 800w, https://theme-fu